{"tid":1433930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢間賣皮嘅店主為食兩家茶飯又扮黃又扮愛黨","createTime":"2019-08-08T15:28:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T02:41:39.000Z","uid":33909,"like":227,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"d6f66fad6ca98ecac33c879b16d2e1f88b52bb40","tid":1433930,"uid":33909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:28:06.000Z","msg":"借朋友個AC開個post幫手宣傳呢個賣皮嘅店主<br />\n<br />\n話緊你呀為咗個幾個臭銀錢連自己嘅立場都出賣埋嘅<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Brothers Leathercraft</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q2FcZnp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq2FcZnp.png&h=b8c9899f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SLOug85.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSLOug85.png&h=f2038c3a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hD391AL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhD391AL.png&h=eae96e69&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8UGceVM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8UGceVM.png&h=addaec94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先係開post話自己扮反中扮撐罷工<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QXoRvuz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQXoRvuz.png&h=c7491bb0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v0DiauA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv0DiauA.png&h=442da68f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YAA8xHW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYAA8xHW.png&h=273d0f5f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0XrWGBh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0XrWGBh.png&h=c68447f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知比人踢爆為賺人仔係淘寶奶共<br />\n奶完大陸狗鞋底又係Fb到扮撐罷工想食兩家茶飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事後又del埋淘寶間鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/344EEoL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F344EEoL.png&h=0d1fb7f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲搵人幫佢澄清，講兩句就想證明自己清白<br />\n良心道歉時間？你估下有冇人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃又好藍又好始終人人有佢自己立場<br />\n但係咁樣真係好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以後剩係賺人仔就得架啦兄弟皮藝"},{"pid":"fe6ab971dce34d02198d837fe30c56a3eac68a76","tid":1433930,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:31:44.000Z","msg":"Fish"},{"pid":"a56618f3fdc9ee091439ade8056f261b753b76ff","tid":1433930,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:32:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0c223591ee5bfbbe070f7fea9cfa949145b8d10","tid":1433930,"uid":121409,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:34:37.000Z","msg":"兩面不是人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4650d884456c225d360b09763b25b15214ced5","tid":1433930,"uid":282634,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:36:06.000Z","msg":"thank you and good bye"},{"pid":"7f5c4f477de13e66b934db0caf531fe035d6caa1","tid":1433930,"uid":8636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e84ec7f601fc022add707144131e8a0a5e381c3","tid":1433930,"uid":146535,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:40:06.000Z","msg":"點解可以咁柒<br />\n同一間舖兩個時空?"},{"pid":"4882ebbcd81835ce65c9feb6607d35def8f43a1a","tid":1433930,"uid":88029,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:43:09.000Z","msg":"此